{"id":2573,"date":"2023-03-29T15:18:16","date_gmt":"2023-03-29T08:18:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2573"},"modified":"2023-09-18T15:20:26","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T08:20:26","slug":"hoc-giao-duc-hoc-la-hoc-lam-giao-vien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/hoc-giao-duc-hoc-la-hoc-lam-giao-vien\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u1eccC GI\u00c1O D\u1ee4C H\u1eccC L\u00c0 H\u1eccC L\u00c0M GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 n\u0103m 2023 m\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ng\u00e0nh Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc, n\u1eafm b\u1eaft xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao trong ng\u00e0nh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 (Thanhdo Education Village) n\u00f3i ri\u00eang.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc, Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 T\u00e2m l\u00fd, gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, sinh vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p ng\u00e0nh Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y: l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p t\u1eeb m\u1ea7m non, ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1eadc \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc; c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c tham v\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd: tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean tham v\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc (gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng), b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n, vi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u00e2m th\u1ea7n, c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Trong qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd: chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, h\u1ecdc v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc (qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd sinh vi\u00ean, qu\u1ea3n sinh, qu\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7m,\u2026), chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty, c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan &#8211; t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c phi ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c\u00a0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u: tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u khoa h\u1ecdc t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c Vi\u1ec7n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u (Vi\u1ec7n Khoa h\u1ecdc X\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, Vi\u1ec7n T\u00e2m l\u00fd h\u1ecdc, Vi\u1ec7n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m\u2026); trung t\u00e2m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u (Trung t\u00e2m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng T\u00e2m l\u00fd h\u1ecdc, Trung t\u00e2m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, Trung t\u00e2m kh\u1ea3o th\u00ed, ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u2026)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0 c\u00e1c Nh\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean theo h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/8Sr8ZRTyNsM\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[ThanhDo Q&amp;A]: \u201c Ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang ngh\u1ec1 &#8211; \u0110i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng\u201d T\u1eadp 1 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u201cGi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc &#8211; Ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc l\u1ea1 m\u00e0 quen\u201d<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00e0nh Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc v\u00ec gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ph\u1ed5 qu\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp l\u00ean cao r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. Theo h\u1ecdc Ng\u00e0nh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m quan tr\u1ecdng cho nh\u1eefng ai d\u00e0nh t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft cho gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc l\u00ean cao hay l\u1ef1a\u00a0 ch\u1ecdn con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng du h\u1ecdc c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean thu\u1ed9c H\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng Song ng\u1eef UNIGO tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho sinh vi\u00ean Ng\u00e0nh Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m ngay ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_12605\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12605\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-12605 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/IMG_1710-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-12605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng Song ng\u1eef UNIGO &#8211; th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a H\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 n\u0103m 2023 m\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ng\u00e0nh Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc, n\u1eafm b\u1eaft xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao trong ng\u00e0nh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":8,"featured_media":2574,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36],"tags":[49,86,42,87],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2573"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/8"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2573"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2573\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2576,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2573\/revisions\/2576"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2574"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2573"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2573"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2573"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}